reviewText: Great video from the In-Fisherman guys. They really show you how to catch more bass with their techniques and the price was awesome.

Older video like the ones you see on tv. There is more catching fish and video of fish being caught than thrre is instruction which is why i gave it two stars. If you want to learn how to finesse fish, youtube is probably a cheaper and better option.
A really helpful video that gets down and really shows you how to rig up. Has a lot of helpful information. worth every penny.
